  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A simple illusion of sight. When hit by an attack, the opponent sees you burst into black raven feathers reforming at your current location. When hit by a melee attack, roll 1d8 reducing damage taken by the result and move 10 feet away. This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p><p>At Higher Levels: This Jutsu's proficiency increases as you increase in level rolling 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 11th level (3d8), 17th level (4d8)</p>",
